name: Easter Leg Warmers
description:
Baby legs are the cutest little accessory to any babies wardrobe!


They are perfect under dresses, tutus, shorts, just with a onesie, or even add them under pants for extra warmth!

-Perfect for those crawlers to protect their little knees!

Unlike tights , they make diaper changes and using the toilet a snap! no need to take them off. Perfect for potty training.

- These baby legs will fit most infants-toddler ... for infants, they will fit at the thigh and will scrunch up. For toddlers, they will fit at or below the knee :-)


Shipping- All items are made and shipped in 48 hours or less. If you are within the U.S, you will receive a tracking number.

All of my items are handmade with love.
